when I saw that birth.

03:31.579 --> 03:35.514
That baby slid out of Erica
with elegance and class

03:35.516 --> 03:38.650
just like Dr. Weem did
in that Mexican booth.

03:38.652 --> 03:41.186
Oh, oh.
(sighs)

03:41.188 --> 03:43.655
