04:31.372 --> 04:32.537
'Cause he lost interest.

04:32.539 --> 04:34.606
(laughs hysterically)

04:39.045 --> 04:41.713
I'm peeing.

04:41.715 --> 04:42.914
I peed a little.

04:42.916 --> 04:44.583
Well, uh, why don't you
clean yourself up

04:44.585 --> 04:45.651
